            <h3>
            Privacy Policy
            <h3>
            <h3>Introduction</h3>
            Bvend Technologies Ltd. wants to create a transparent relationship with its Users. Therefore this section is dedicated to helping Users understand how we collect, use, share and store their information. 
            <h3>Information Collection</h3>
            We collect User’s phone number and bkash account number to create a cashless vending experience. We collect this information let Users access/use our service, to verify identity for account access and payments, and to improve our service. A User needs to provide this information only during registration of their account. This information is not optional and without providing this information a User will not be able to gain access or use our application.
            <h3>Information Usage</h3>
            When a User signs up with a phone number we use it to send one-time password, to keep log of the User and to assist with payments. We do not sell or share User’s information to third parties without User’s consent. We share transaction records to make sales reports for our Vendors to help them better understand Users’ consumption behavior. This way a Vendor can know Users’ demand and enhance their vending business. 
            <h3>Information Storage</h3>
            Unless otherwise required by law, Bvend Technologies Ltd. will only retain User information for as long as a User wishes to maintain their account. 
            <h3>Updates in policies</h3>
            We might make changes to these privacy policies as well as publish additional policies. Any such update will be notified to our Users through the application and website. We suggest our Users view the Privacy Policy section time to time to stay updated. 
